data.Bio: &quot;Mr. Karan Khajuria is an Assistant Professor at the Model Institute of Engineering and Technology, Jammu in the Department of Computer Science &amp; Engineering. He has done his Masters in Software Engineering from the Indian Institute of Information Technology(IIIT), Trichy, Tamil Nadu, and Bachelor&#039;s in Computer Science &amp; Engineering from Shri Mata Vaishno Devi University, Katra, Jammu &amp; Kashmir. His areas of interest include AI, NLP, IoT, and Data Analytics. He has filed 4 patents at the IPTO. He is also a part of the Centre for Sofware Development(CSDIS) as a manager and Training and Placement Cell as a technical mentor. &quot;
data.PG_Institute: Indian Institute of Information Technology Tiruchirappalli
